text: I want to give thanks to God for guiding us to this church.. It's a pleasure and thank you for your warm welcome. Thanks to Rev Stephen Lim for his sharing, to make me understand to become Martha and Mary in my working life. Let us glory honour to Our Lord
Accessible from Teck Ghee (AMK) via a tunnel under the CTE.
Long time see this church in my life
